  "texts": [
    "The advantage of having its own HKUST ChatGPT is that it can implement encryption measures to protect confidential information shared during the chat, further protecting the intellectual knowledge of its staff and students.While the search period of this study lasted until the end of July 2023, the authors failed to search for more related news articles after the above event.",
    "One of the possible reasons is that an increased number of universities have been welcoming the use of ChatGPT and other GenAI tools, therefore, it lost the \"news\" value to be reported.",
    "For instance, in July 2023, Lingnan University launched Lingnan ChatGPT and announced the allowance of using ChatGPT in the 2023-24 academic year, but it was not covered in the news media.",
    "However, given that universities are starting to benchmark with others on this matter, it is not unreasonable to expect that their policy and practices will become more similar.",
    "However, this study has captured the significant events and challenges encountered by the universities during the most intense period of change."
